<L>__{interior hotel lobby. day}
<A>__{the lobby buzzes with activity. at the reception, gregoire is surrounded by a bbc news crew: gloria, young, chic female reporter producer, and jock, tough, experienced scottish cameraman, and his local sound guy peter. gloria is upset.}
